				<td colspan="2"><span>Hi Folks !
<br />

<br />
Happens to me all the time.
<br />

<br />
When they introduced the new combat ability system they mapped the disciplines to several keys ( ctrl 1 - crtl 4 for our 4 disciplines )
<br />

<br />
Usually I twist my songs with the regular hotkey keys ( 1 - 0 ). To position myself i use the cursor keys and I use strave very often ( ctrl crsr left / right ).
<br />

<br />
So some times I am straving ( ctrl pressed ) and try to twist a song ( by hitting keys 1 to 4 ) I am activating the corresponding discipline ( ctrl 1 - 4 )
<br />

<br />
That is what i think is happening to you, too.
<br />

<br />
I remapped Deftdance and Puretone, but I am too lazy to remap Fearless and Resistence so they get off several times per session.
<br />

<br />
Baba
<br />

<br />
